e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"728要聲討！"},{"pid":"ac02a05e9d20b27670dbb27379a23dc2810f3962","tid":1357640,"uid":11903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:53:59.000Z","msg":"推到班黑警仆街"},{"pid":"dc27fbac21721dd1d454c6e89580ff06738d4ed0","tid":1357640,"uid":4700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"要令更多人知！推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n「長期置頂」727元朗反鄉黑遊行終極攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356464</a><br />\n<br />\n【上熱門呀】元朗遊行詳細po，推正經po啦，咪再講好多垃圾po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356135</a><br />\n<br />\n［727元朗］我係勇武，我有野想講（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357351</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全部同我入撚曬黎）成個運動越黎越亂，小弟忍唔住，有D野一定要講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357282</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[請長期置頂] 民間保衛隊初形 公民團結行公義 任何抗命運動適用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351343</a><br />\n<br />\n【文宣包】同我入黎！721西環宣言！上環36槍！文宣打包哂俾你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356661</a><br />\n<br />\n西上環事件整合 求更多新聞同義士消息 推上去 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357053</a><br />\n<br />\n721 開槍時間與影片整理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356665</a><br />\n<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n<br />\n【721上環警方暴力清場合集】3分鐘足本版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357640</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲<br />\n5. 全面實行雙普選</span>"},{"pid":"a11dc553ab263a20d90e8a62f66750f828bde16c","tid":1357640,"uid":284559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:54:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83380f806f1c3827bc84fd71fab2becc24d2a986","tid":1357640,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75198e28f43eddfc85b01fec338a4e6d1204bb0","tid":1357640,"uid":98038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1968db21ecae54e5eb64b7ed962f32508962cc","tid":1357640,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:44:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 7.27 元朗反黑遊行 </span><br />\n（和平示威 但對方郁我哋係必須還手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n（朝早11點 元朗西鐵集合）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 7.28 上環追究開槍大遊行</span><br />\n（7.21 當晚無預警開槍 開咗最少36槍）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（仲有一位前線係醫院危殆中）</span><br />\n（香港人 你唔出黎 你好唔好意思？）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:50:50.000Z","msg":"元朗 27定28定兩日都有啊 <br />\n媽啊好亂啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:55:00.000Z","msg":"27"},{"pid":"20b3b2ec966ea6d291960a00eafb405bc39d765e","tid":1357640,"uid":176864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:59:49.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a6cd376d07f9c6de359204c7a2c51c5e70e927a8","tid":1357640,"uid":15360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死黑警"},{"pid":"7300e917faeb2dfe2996dc6e4c5089b2933557ed","tid":1357640,"uid":181269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19: